004package data;
005
006public class ValBool extends Val {
007  boolean value;
008
009  public ValBool(boolean val) {
010    value = val;
011  }
012
013  @Override
014  public boolean getBool () {
015    return value;
016  }
017
018  @Override
019  public String toString () {
020    return String.valueOf(value);
021  }
022}
